{"tid":242664,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[㷫過火屎!!!] 有無絲打另一半都好口賤????","createTime":"2017-05-14T05:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T12:13:41.000Z","uid":431,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1fd1c2aa3b2b489f9fce2e649225fb9cccf1cc2","tid":242664,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:48:55.000Z","msg":"佢對其他人係點我唔知<br />\n但對住我好嗰時好好，鬧親交就幾仆街都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我份人又小器乜都記到實<br />\n雖然事後佢會氹返我sa lum話無下次但都係不停loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個心已經有條刺了唔知佢講嘅賤嘢係借住鬧交講事實定鬥氣說話。。。<br />\n我都表明過好多次唔鍾意，佢話會改但每次都一樣<br />\n好似琴晚咁唔記得佢講咩激我<br />\n我就問：「點解你把口可以咁撚臭？」<br />\n之後佢居然答：「奶過你個閪緊係臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n嘩我當堂嬲到震!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁想串佢話俾你屌過咪臭啲!!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底點先可以令佢把口無咁衰，有時佢話係戲言但都太過份了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我嬲又話唔明我嬲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40b5c437b729e937824b7fec3e7ba7b6b30d139","tid":242664,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T05:52:54.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7edcbda4e973a7e9e66110dd30cc256cb269bb59","tid":2